# Day 8: Cost Monitoring and Optimization with CloudWatch and Budgets

**Goal:** To set up CloudWatch alarms for resource utilization and create budgets to track spending. Configure a report on cost per service using Cost Explorer.

**Solution:** I configured CloudWatch alarms to monitor CPU usage of an EC2 instance, set an AWS budget to track spending, and I used Cost Explorer to track cost per service.

**AWS Services Used:** CloudWatch, AWS Budgets, Cost Explorer

**Key Learnings:** I learned how to use CloudWatch for resource monitoring, how to create notifications, and how to use AWS Budgets to control spending, and how to track costs per service.

**Challenges and Solutions:** There were no particular challenges with this project.